  "text": "# BRANCHES & LOCATIONS  \n**Q: Where are FirstUK branches?**\nA: 12 branches across the UK:\n- **London:** Canary Wharf + Head Office (Threadneedle Street)\n- **North West:** Manchester, Liverpool\n- **Midlands:** Birmingham\n- **North East:** Leeds\n- **South:** Bristol, Southampton\n- **Scotland:** Edinburgh, Glasgow\n- **East:** Norwich\n- **Ireland:** Belfast  \n**Q: What are branch opening hours?**\nA: Monday–Friday 09:00–17:00, Saturday 09:00–13:00 (closed Sundays/bank holidays).  \n**Q: Can I visit without an appointment?**\nA: Yes, walk-ins welcome. For complex matters, book an appointment (call 0800-555-2265).  \n---",
